129
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:52,510
When we were leaving,
it was almost as dark as it is now.

130
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,830
You were so scared you almost cried.

131
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:54,750
I was also terrified.

132
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:56,710
Ouch!

133
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:58,680
Oh.

134
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:15,190
Hey, hey, hey.

135
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,630
Are you okay?

136
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,550
It hurts. It hurts.

137
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,510
Chen Xi.

138
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,320
What are you doing?

139
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,270
You look pretty rich.

140
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,430
I want to get some money
from you to buy cigarettes.

141
00:08:39,150 --> 00:08:40,350
Xinyue, let's go.

142
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,710
- Hey, Chen Xi.
- Xinyue.

143
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,560
Xinyue.

144
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,520
- Let go!
- Let go of me!

145
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:47,520
Chen Xi.

146
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,680
Let go!

147
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:51,400
Ah!

148
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:52,870
Xinyue.

149
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:53,830
