155
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,270
- I'm fine.
- Let's go.

156
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,240
Okay.

157
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,270
If you want money, that's fine.

158
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:42,120
Chen Xi.

159
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:05,720
Chen Xi.

160
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,150
