161
00:10:08,150 --> 00:10:09,160
- and got a gunshot wound.
- Chen Xi.

162
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,320
He can't have gone far.

163
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,430
- Xinyue.
- Hurry and chase him.

164
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:17,400
Help...

165
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,230
Where is he? I just saw him.

166
